{"tid":1221292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[五獨聯合] 東突 : 香港加油 維吾爾人民與你們同在","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T12:53:43.000Z","uid":24140,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f555aede5f075d3a664283efd27e04865cc5587b","tid":1221292,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:24:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/turkistaner/status/1139052978663493638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fturkistaner%2Fstatus%2F1139052978663493638&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=ee7191a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fturkistaner%2Fstatus%2F1139052978663493638&h=7c119d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/turkistaner/status/1139052978663493638</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKMjGaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKMjGaG.jpg&h=6ad8eb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾經在香港待過一周，那邊給我的感覺就是很自由、很民主、很開放，那邊的百姓給我的感覺就是很友善。香港百姓曾經為維吾爾人、為關閉集中營而遊行過，推特上好多香港朋友支持過我們的自由和獨立。<br />\n在此，我代表身邊的朋友支持香港的遊行，支持香港的法制，支持香港的自由！"},{"pid":"63db74bdc7b3a28ced6efb7f59670a85dcfeceb7","tid":1221292,"uid":242805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似好堅咁，玩轉個Party<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57b43f70a76a06f89510faffb479fc71c1b4074","tid":1221292,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-1